        "Title": "LFC #28 Blindness and Sight",
        "Location": "LOCATION_MARRAKECH",
        "PublicId": "106248491672",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/marrakesh/_scene_spider.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ca967a22-8b3a-406a-b7d9-788fb9f56d01).Image",
        "Description": "Sayid Laham is a terrorist known for random bombings. He wears a mask out of a twisted philosophy: if he cannot see his victims, his justice is blind.\rHe was caught when a photographer took a picture of his face. This happened soon after the photographer&apos;s wife fell to one of his attacks.\rEach wants poetic revenge on the other. The photographer wants Laham to die by a bomb. Laham wants the photographer shot. It is perhaps cruel to accept both contracts, 47. But the pay is all the same.\rBy Quinez",
